</ul>
<h4 id="toc7"><span>Tales:</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/a-greater-darkness">A Greater Darkness</a> - <em>They had come early, early in the afternoon - but of course they had. The early afternoon is benevolent. No one wants to hurt you at two in the afternoon. No one wants to kill you, or tear you to pieces, when the sun is high in the sky.</em> Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fastandbulbous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2139686); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2139686&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869440" alt="fastandbulbous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2139686)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fastandbulbous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2139686); return false;">fastandbulbous</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/disinformation-bureau-orientation">Disinformation Bureau Orientation</a> - Learn to be the Man in Black to the Men in Black. Covered by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lazar-lyusternik" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2326669); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2326669&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869440" alt="Lazar Lyusternik" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2326669)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lazar-lyusternik" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2326669); return false;">Lazar Lyusternik</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc8"><span>Hubs:</span></h4>
